---
---

<section class="s-white" style="padding:140px 0 60px;">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="auth-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:16px">Über uns</p>
      <h2 class="auth-h2">
        Nicht irgendein Tool.<br/>
        <em class="italic-gradient">Gebaut von Leuten, die es selbst machen.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="auth-grid">
      <div class="auth-text reveal-left">
        <p class="auth-body">
          Julian und ich besitzen selbst über 150 Einheiten. Über 400 Millionen Euro
          Transaktionsvolumen. Als wir unsere eigenen Portfolios mit der KI durchgerechnet
          haben, war das ein Schock — auch bei uns lag Geld auf dem Tisch. Genau deshalb
          haben wir ImmoIQ gebaut.
        </p>
        <div class="auth-author">
          <div class="auth-avatar">MB</div>
          <div>
            <p class="auth-name">Max Bertlein</p>
            <p class="auth-role">Gründer · WBD Gruppe · 150+ eigene Einheiten</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-badges">
          <span class="auth-badge">📺 Amazon Prime „The Mittelstand"</span>
          <span class="auth-badge">🏢 WBD Gruppe</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Real testimonial -->
      <div class="auth-testimonial reveal-right">
        <div class="card auth-quote-card">
          <div class="auth-quote-top">
            <span class="auth-stars">★★★★★</span>
            <span class="auth-result">+12.400€/Jahr</span>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="auth-quote">
            „Allein durch die Steueroptimierung fast 12.000 Euro im ersten Jahr gespart.
            Und das bei nur 4 Einheiten. Der Report war auf den Euro genau — kein Vergleich
            zu dem was mein Steuerberater bisher gesagt hat."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="auth-quote-author">
            <div class="auth-quote-avatar">TK</div>
            <div>
              <p class="auth-quote-name">Thomas K.</p>
              <p class="auth-quote-info">4 Einheiten · München</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .auth-header { margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .auth-h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 48px); line-height: 1.1; margin: 0; }

  .auth-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) { .auth-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: start; } }

  .auth-body { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 32px; }

  .auth-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .auth-avatar {
    width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--text); color: #fff;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .auth-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; margin: 0; }
  .auth-role { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 2px 0 0; }

  .auth-badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
  .auth-badge {
    padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--light); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* Testimonial card */
  .auth-quote-card { padding: 36px; }
  .auth-quote-top {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .auth-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .auth-result {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--green);
  }
  .auth-quote {
    font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 24px; font-style: normal;
  }
  .auth-quote-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .auth-quote-avatar {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--light); color: var(--text);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .auth-quote-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; }
  .auth-quote-info { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 2px 0 0; }
</style>
